Class InteractableWorld

java.lang.Object
com.fy916.bubblebobble.gaming.world.InteractableWorld
public class InteractableWorld extends Object
InteractableWorld includes the WorldElements and the bacis property of the game world such as friction, gravity, etc.

  • Constructor Details

    • InteractableWorld

      public InteractableWorld​(int input_unit_width, int input_unit_height, int input_unit_size)
      Initialize the game world for Objects to move and display in
      Parameters:
      input_unit_width - The Unit Width of the game world, note this is not the exact window size but the relevant size
      input_unit_height - The Unit Height of the game world, note this is not the exact window size but the relevant size
      input_unit_size - The Unit Size of the game world, the window size is the unit width/height times the unit size
